         1 INTRODUCTION
+        _ ____________

        SMART  IS DESIGNED TO ALLOW  USERS TO PRODUCE  AND MAINTAIN MANU
   OR REPORTS.   SMART WILL  AUTOMATICALLY PRODUCE  THE TABLE  OF CONTEN
   PRINT PAGE HEADINGS,  PRODUCE AN INDEX,  CHECK WORD SPELLING,  AND OT
   FACILITIES  WHICH ARE  DESIGNED TO  MAKE DOCUMENTING  AN  EASIER  CHO
   SMART IS NOT A TEXT EDITOR, ONLY A MANUAL PRINTER.  THEREFORE,  YOU W
   NEED A TEXT EDITOR, SUCH A TSO EDIT, TO CREATE YOUR REPORT.    THE IN
   TO SMART IS A 80 BYTE RECORD IN WHICH ONLY THE FIRST 72 COLUMNS ARE U
   THEREFORE THE MAXIMUM LINE WIDTH IS 72. ALTHOUGH THIS MANUAL IS IN UP
   CASE, MANUALS MAY HAVE EITHER UPPER OR LOWER CASE CHARACTERS. IF YOU
   USING TSO SPF EDIT, THE TE, TS,  AND TF COMMANDS ARE VERY HELPFUL AND
   MAY BE WISE FOR YOU TO INVESTIGATE THE USE OF THESE COMMANDS.  SMART
   DESIGNED  TO WORK ON THE IBM 3800 LASER PRINTER,  BUT THERE IS NO REA
   WHY IT  SHOULD NOT WORK  PROPERLY ON ANY  OTHER TYPE  OF PRINTER.
   PROGRAM NUMBER FOR SMART IS SFT8MV74.

